## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8129-102">이러한 이벤트가 발생 하는 경우는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType> 및 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType> 의 인스턴스를 전달 하는 이벤트 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs> 관련된 된 이벤트에 대 한 처리기를 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8129-102">When they are raised, the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType> events pass an instance of  <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs> to  the handler for the associated event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8129-103"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs.AudioLevel%2A> 오디오 새 수준을 입력 될 때 속성을 가져옵니다 합니다 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType> 또는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType> 이벤트가 발생 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8129-103">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs.AudioLevel%2A> property gets the new level of audio input when the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType> event is raised.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8129-104">`AudioLevel` 의 속성을 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> 및 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> 클래스는 현재 음성 인식 엔진에 대 한 오디오 입력 수준을 제공 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8129-104">The `AudioLevel` property of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> classes provides the current level of the audio input to the speech recognition engine.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8129-105">다음 예제에서는 이벤트 처리기를 추가 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8129-105">The following example adds an event handler to a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a8129-106">처리기는 콘솔에 새 오디오 수준을 출력합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8129-106">The handler outputs the new audio level to the console.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a8129-107"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs>은 <xref:System.EventArgs>로부터 파생됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a8129-107"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs> derives from <xref:System.EventArgs>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
  
private SpeechRecognitionEngine sre;  
  
// Initialize the SpeechRecognitionEngine object.   
private void Initialize()  
{  
  sre = new SpeechRecognitionEngine();  
  
  // Add an event handler for the AudioLevelUpdated event.  
  sre.AudioLevelUpdated += new EventHandler<AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs>(sre_AudioLevelUpdated);  
  
  // Add other initialization code here.  
}  
  
// Write the audio level to the console when the AudioLevelUpdated event is raised.  
void sre_AudioLevelUpdated(object sender, AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs e)  
{  
  Console.WriteLine("The audio level is now: {0}.", e.AudioLevel);  
}  
  
```
